WEBVTT

00:00.677 --> 00:01.227
Hello?

00:01.941 --> 00:02.454
Hello?

00:02.843 --> 00:03.656
This is David.

00:04.071 --> 00:05.380
Can I speak to Amanda?

00:05.751 --> 00:07.191
This is Amanda speaking.

00:07.625 --> 00:08.391
Hi Amanda.

00:08.734 --> 00:09.629
How are you today?

00:10.029 --> 00:10.825
I'm good.

00:11.234 --> 00:12.145
That's good to hear.

00:12.554 --> 00:13.535
Did you have lunch?

00:13.695 --> 00:15.088
Yes, I had lunch.

00:15.669 --> 00:16.860
What did you have for lunch?

00:17.195 --> 00:20.317
I had pizza, salad and Coke for lunch.

00:20.697 --> 00:23.060
Wow, that sounds very delicious!

00:23.360 --> 00:23.908
Yes.

00:24.129 --> 00:25.601
It was very yummy.

00:26.193 --> 00:27.786
What kind of pizza did you have?

00:28.118 --> 00:29.624
I had cheese pizza.

00:29.920 --> 00:32.027
Oh, it makes me very hungry.

00:32.380 --> 00:33.739
Do you like Italian food?

00:34.160 --> 00:37.649
Yes, but I usually have Korean food for lunch.

00:38.156 --> 00:39.891
What is your favorite Korean food?

00:40.176 --> 00:43.035
My favorite Korean food is kimchi jjigae.

00:43.639 --> 00:44.642
How does it taste?

00:45.539 --> 00:47.123
Oh, you mean kimchi jjigae?

00:47.749 --> 00:49.181
It's hot and spicy.

00:50.397 --> 00:52.145
Maybe you need water when you eat.

